As a home cook, I need to add a new recipe with a title, ingredients, and instructions, so that I can save my favorite dishes.
As a home cook, I need to see a list of all my saved recipes, so that I can quickly browse my collection.
As a home cook, I need to view the full details (ingredients, instructions) of a specific recipe, so that I can follow it while cooking.
As a home cook, I need to be able to edit an existing recipe's title, ingredients, or instructions, so that I can correct errors or make improvements.
As a home cook, I need to be able to delete a recipe, so that I can remove recipes I no longer want to keep.
As a home cook, I need to search for recipes by keywords in their title or ingredients, so that I can quickly find specific dishes.
